release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 3.8.x -->

## What's Changed

## Dependency Upgrades 🚀

* micronaut-openapi to 4.8.2 (#8656)
* micronaut-oracle-cloud to 2.3.2 (#8658)

### Bug Fixes 🐞
* Handle WebLogic classloader URIs by @mattmoss in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8646
* Fix Cors for alternate local addresses by @timyates in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8642

* Fixed property placeholder expression issue (#8633) by @msupic in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8645

### Docs 📖
* chore(doc): upgrade lombok patch version by @juanpabloprado in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8648

### CI ⚙️
* ci: sync as in project template by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8671

## New Contributors
* @msupic made their first contribution in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8645
* @juanpabloprado made their first contribution in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/8648

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v3.8.2...v3.8.3
